182
00:11:48,788 --> 00:11:50,688
Bisakah kau menghentikannya?

183
00:11:50,688 --> 00:11:52,688
Tidakkah kau ingat apa yang Sonoko katakan?

184
00:11:52,688 --> 00:11:54,188
