235
00:14:46,688 --> 00:14:48,788
KIX.

236
00:14:48,788 --> 00:14:49,988
Apa?

237
00:14:49,988 --> 00:14:53,488
Kau tahu apa artinya ini?

238
00:14:53,488 --> 00:14:57,788
